<dl id="n12114g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12114g">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12114g"> 114(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> penitential</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Jonas se pla&icirc;t &agrave; raconter ces nouvelles qui l&apos;int&eacute;ressaient grandement, non moins que ses contemporains. Il est plus sobre de d&eacute;tails sur le r&ocirc;le, pourtant d&apos;une extr&ecirc;me cons&eacute;quence, que son h&eacute;ros joua dans l&apos;affermissement de la vie morale et dans l&apos;&eacute;volution du r&eacute;gime p&eacute;nitentiel. <br><font color="green">[No less than his contemporaries, Jonas took pleasure in recounting the stories that he was greatly interested in. He is more measured about the details of the role played by his hero, which was however of great consequence, in strengthening moral life and in the evolution of the <mark>penitential</mark> system.]</font> <small> <a name="STCM" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#STCM"><cite title="source">Saint Colomban</cite></a> (1905) 69</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
